{"tid":746554,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲做運輸處？海外轉香港牌一問","createTime":"2018-07-17T15:33:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T04:52:59.000Z","uid":86808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ce7e44e242596704be7e5596abbc3822443a2bbc","tid":746554,"uid":86808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T15:33:41.000Z","msg":"想問下我想將澳洲牌轉番香港牌，但係可唔可以係海外寄文件申請？<br />\n<br />\n根據td個網<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.td.gov.hk/tc/public_services/licences_and_permits/driving_licences/how_to_apply_for_a_driving_licence/driving_in_hong_kong_for_overseas_driving_licence_/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.td.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fpublic_services%2Flicences_and_permits%2Fdriving_licences%2Fhow_to_apply_for_a_driving_licence%2Fdriving_in_hong_kong_for_overseas_driving_licence_%2Findex.html&d=7f2ZIAzAuNvc8Kmrht0lyf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=e69ee900\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.td.gov.hk/tc/public_services/licences_and_permits/driving_licences/how_to_apply_for_a_driving_licence/driving_in_hong_kong_for_overseas_driving_licence_/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote> 3.1.3 所需文件及費用 ?<br />\n      \t<br />\n香港身份證﹝正本及副本﹞；<br />\n      \t<br />\n有關旅遊證件﹝例如護照﹞﹝正本及副本﹞；<br />\n      \t<br />\n有關海外駕駛執照﹝正本及副本﹞；<br />\n \t<br />\n如該海外駕駛執照並非以英文或中文書寫，則須一併遞交經官方認可的譯本；<br />\n \t<br />\n其他有關證明文件﹝正本及副本﹞；<br />\n \t<br />\n現時地址的證明（住址及通訊地址）正本或副本；<br />\n \t<br />\n註冊醫生簽發的運輸署體格檢驗證書 TD256 ﹝只適用於七十歲或以上的申請人﹞；及<br />\n \t<br />\n所需費用﹝可於各牌照事務處詢問處查詢、致電 1823 電話中心查詢、參閱牌照事務處的牌照費用表 (TD341)，或瀏覽運輸署 網頁 ﹞。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢所有野都要正本<br />\n但係啲正本係曬我呢邊（因為我係澳洲⋯咁好正常跟住我）<br />\n我所有文件都有太平紳士certified copy<br />\n咁樣可唔可以取代正本？<br />\n<br />\n海外打唔到去1823<br />\n唯有係度碰下運氣"},{"pid":"9c0bc02332af5a20fd2aac49cccb54c57f51301c","tid":746554,"uid":32901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T15:37:23.000Z","msg":"得閒返香港先轉"},{"pid":"f8734734bd19e23c9a0ea85c7e0325e189fe12e9","tid":746554,"uid":86808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c0bc02332af5a20fd2aac49cccb54c57f51301c","tid":746554,"uid":32901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T15:37:23.000Z","msg":"得閒返香港先轉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T15:39:00.000Z","msg":"我會番香港一個禮拜，夠唔夠時間比我整完+渣車？"},{"pid":"e96d6f9f6a3d4e7792987a72814563401dd3fef7","tid":746554,"uid":89801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T15:42:27.000Z","msg":"如果樓主有睇清楚 應該唔會問呢個問題<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/234158_393ef9c32865705548c6173d148b4e4f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F234158_393ef9c32865705548c6173d148b4e4f.png&h=3a84d857&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d5072256994cf72b95479fb4f7efceca635daf7","tid":746554,"uid":89801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e96d6f9f6a3d4e7792987a72814563401dd3fef7","tid":746554,"uid":89801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T15:42:27.000Z","msg":"如果樓主有睇清楚 應該唔會問呢個問題<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/234158_393ef9c32865705548c6173d148b4e4f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F234158_393ef9c32865705548c6173d148b4e4f.png&h=3a84d857&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T15:44:36.000Z","msg":"政府野寫得好清楚<br />\n「交回」同「寄回」係好大分別"},{"pid":"e01aa9c63574c11a08cedefbafdfb9e98a31865a","tid":746554,"uid":89801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T15:47:41.000Z","msg":"如果樓主認為網站寫得唔清楚<br />\n可能你認為郵寄都算係「交回」既其中一個方法<br />\n<br />\n如果你有睇過申請表<br />\n係絕對唔會開呢個post問<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/234733_411a4a16ed05f33ae4eb3be58cc085dd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F234733_411a4a16ed05f33ae4eb3be58cc085dd.png&h=3f52ece4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a9c202